><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Heidegger, Martin. 1962. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Being and Time</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Trs. John Macquarrie and Edward Robinson. Oxford: Blackwell Publishing.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Herbert, George. 1961. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The Poems of George Herbert</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Ed. Helen Gardner, London: Oxford University Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Hill. Geoffrey, interviewed by Carl Phillips. 2000. ‘</span><a href="http://www.theparisreview.org/interviews/730/the-art-of-poetry-no-80-geoffrey-hill"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">The A</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">r</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">t of Poetry, No. 80</span></a><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">’, </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Paris Revie</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">w 154, Spring. </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Hopkins, Gerard Manley. 1959. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The Journals and Papers of Gerard Manley Hopkins</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Humphrey House, ed. London: Oxford University Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Hopson, Janet L. 1998.</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;"> </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">‘Fetal Psychology’, </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Psychology Today</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">, October.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">http://www.leaderu.com/orgs/tul/psychtoday9809.html, consulted January 21, 2009.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Hughes, Ted. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1970 [1967] </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Poetry in the Making</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. London: Faber and Faber.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———, i</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">nterviewed by Drue Heinz. 1995. ‘</span><a href="http://www.theparisreview.org/interviews/1669/the-art-of-poetry-no-71-ted-hughes"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">The Art of </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">P</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;text-decoration: underline;">oetry No. 71’</span></a><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">, </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The Paris Review </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">134, Spring. </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:1.4pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Ivanov, V. V. &amp; V. I. Toporov. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1974. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Issledovanya v oblasti slavyanskih drevnotstei</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;"> [</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Researches in the Field of Slavonic Antiquities/Folklore</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">], subtitled </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Lexical and phraseological questions in the reconstruction of texts</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Moscow: Izdaetelstvo ‘Nauka’.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Jakobson, Roman. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1949.</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;"> ‘Slavic Mythology’, Funk and Wagnell’s</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;"> Standard Dictionary of Folklore, Mythology and Legend</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">, eds. Leach M. and Fried J., Vol. 2: 1025-8. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">New York: Harper and Row</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1985. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Collected Works</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">, </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Vol. VII</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">, Berlin, New York and Amsterdam: Mouton Publishers. </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1964. ‘Linguistic Evidence in Comparative Mythology’. Moscow.  1964. </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Jonson, Ben</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1959. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Five Plays</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. London: Oxford University Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Jope, Norman, Paul Scott Derrick and Catherine E. Byfield, eds. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Salt Companion to Richard Berengarten</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Cambridge: Salt Publishing. 2011.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Jung, C. G. 1956. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Symbols of Transformation: Collected Works: 5</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Tr. R. F. C. Hull. London: Routledge and Kegan Paul.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1968 [1951]. ‘Foreword’ to </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The I Ching: the Richard Wilhelm Translation</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">, English tr. Cary F. Baynes. London: Routledge and Kegan Paul.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1969 [1960]. ‘The Stages of Life’. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The Structure and Dynamics of the Psyche: Collected Works: 8</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Tr. R. F. C. Hull. London: Routledge &amp; Kegan Paul.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1969 [1960]. ‘Synchronicity: An Acausal Connecting Principle’,</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;"> The Structure and Dynamics of the Psyche</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">: </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Collected Works</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">:</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;"> 8</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Tr. R. F. C. Hull. London: Routledge &amp; Kegan Paul.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Jung, C. G. &amp; Pauli, W. 1955. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">The Interpretation of Nature and the Psyche</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Tr. R. F. C. Hull. London: Routledge &amp; Kegan Paul.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Karadžić, Vuk Stefanović. 1852 [1818]. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Srpski Rječnik</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;"> [</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Serbian Dictionary</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">]. Vienna: Typis Congretationis Mechitaristicae / Jermenskoga Namastira.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1957 [1867]. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#FF0000;"> </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Život i običaji naroda srpskoga </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">[</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Life and Customs of the Serbian People</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">]. Belgrade: Srpska književna zadruga.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Lieberman,</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;"> </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Philip. 1967. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Intonation,</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Perception and Language</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Research Monograph No. 38, Cambridge, Massachusetts: M. I. T. Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1975. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">On the Origins of Language</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. New York: Macmillan.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1977. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Speech Physiology and Acoustic Phonetics</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. New York: Macmillan.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">1998. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Eve Spoke</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">, New York: W. W, Norton. </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">———— ———. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">2006. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Toward an Evolutionary Biology of Language</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Cambridge, Massachusetts: Belknap Press of Harvard University Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Mandelstam Osip. 1977. ‘About an interlocutor’. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Selected Essays</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. Tr. Sydney Monas, Austin: University of Texas Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">Main, Roderick. 2007. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Revelations of Chance: Synchronicity as Spiritual Experience</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">. New York: State University of New York Press,</span></p><p style="margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;">Olson, Charles. 1970 [1960]. </span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;font-style: italic;">The Maximus Poems</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;">.  London : Cape Goliard Press.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;margin-left:85.05pt;text-indent:-85.05pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding: 1pt 4pt;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;font-style: italic;">Oxford English Dictionary online</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;">.</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;color:#0000FF;"> </span></p><p style="text-ali